import Vue from 'vue'
import Router from 'vue-router'
import Home from '@/views/home'

Vue.use(Router)

/* Router Modules */
import userRouter from './modules/user'
import articleRouter from './modules/artcile'
import questionRouter from './modules/question'
import topicRouter from './modules/topic'
import exerciseRouter from './modules/exercise'
import videoRouter from './modules/video'


export default new Router({
    mode: 'history',
    base: process.env.BASE_URL,
    routes: [
        {
            path: '/',
            name: 'home',
            component: Home
        },
        articleRouter,
        questionRouter,
        topicRouter,
        exerciseRouter,
        videoRouter,
        userRouter
    ]
})
